Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim BBA_EQP As String
BBA_EQP = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO = Mid(BBA_EQP, 2, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "-" Then BBA_EQP_TIPO = Left(BBA_EQP, 1) BBA_EQP_NUMERO = Mid(BBA_EQP, 3) Else BBA_EQP_TIPO = Left(BBA_EQP, 3) BBA_EQP_NUMERO = Mid(BBA_EQP, 8, 8) + "_" + Mid(BBA_EQP, 17, 1) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & BBA_EQP_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & BBA_EQP_NUMERO & "'"
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & BBA_EQP_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & BBA_EQP_NUMERO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
